OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChristmas strikes don't    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmake me a Grinch - union   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fboss                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of a rail workers union has   
OL,6, said he is "not the Grinch" ahead of   
OL,7, fresh strikes in the run-up to         
OL,8, Christmas and after New Year.          
OL,10,FMick Lynch, general secretary of the   
OL,11,FRMT Union, said the latest walkouts    
OL,12,Fwould "show how important our members  
OL,13,Fare to the running of this country".   
OL,15,FPassengers are expected to face major  
OL,16,Fdisruption over the festive period.    
OL,18,FThe strikes will be staged across four 
OL,19,F48-hour periods on 13-14 and 16-17     
OL,20,FDecember, and 3-4 and 6-7 January.     
